      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas astotajs astotā Meh-\nneſi bija Sibekajus tas Ufatite-\nris no teem Saritereem/ un eekſch\nwinna Kahrtas bija diwidefinits\ntſchetr tuhkſtoſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas dewitajs dewitā\nMehneſi bija Abtēſers tas Anto-\ntiteris/ no teem Benjamitereem/\nun eekſch winna Kahrtas bija di-\nwidefinits tſchetr tuhkſtoſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas deſmitajs deſmitā\nMehneſi bija Maērajuś tas Ne-\ntowatiteris / starp teem Sarite-\nreem/ un eekſch winna Kahrtas bi-\nja diwidefinits tſchetr tuhkſtoſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas weenpadefinitajs\nweenpadeſmitā Mehneſi bija\nBenajns tas Pirgatoniteris no\nEewrāima Behrneem/ un eekſch\nwinna Kahrtas bija diwidefinits\ntſchetr tuhkſtoſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas diwipadefinitajs di-\nwi padeſmitā Mehneſi bija El-\nDajus tas Netowatiteris/ no Ot-\nniēta/ un eekſch winna Kahrtas\nbija diwidefinits tſchetr tuhk-\nſtoſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet pahr Israēta Ziltin\nbija : Pahr teem Rubbenitereem\nbija par Walditaju Eliējers Sik-\nra Dehls. Pahr teem Sihme-\nunitereem bija Sewatijus Ma-\neka Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahr teem Lewiteem bija\nAsabijus Remnēta Dehls. Pahr\nteem Aaronitereem bija Zadaſs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahr Juhda bija Eliju\nno Dahwida Brahkeem: Pa-\nIhsafcharu bija Omrus Mi-\neka Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahr Sebulanu bija Z\nmajus Obadija Dehls. Pa-\nNawtalu bija Jeremots Asr-\nta Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahr Gewrāima Be-\nneem bija Oseus Asafia Deh-\nPahr to puſs Zilti Manaff-\nbija Joels Pedaja Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahr to puſs Zilti M-\nnaffus eekſch Gileadas bija\ndus Sakarija Dehls. Pahr B-\njaminu bija Jaēsiels Abn-\nDehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahr Dann bija Aſa-\nels Jeroaima Dehls: Schee\nto Israēta Ziltu Wirfneeki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Dahwids ne lih-\nnaja tohs/ kas diwidefinits G-\ndus wezzi un wehl jaunaki bi-\ntapehz ka tas KUNGS bij-\nzijs / ka tas gribbetu Isra-\nwairoht/ ka tahs Debbes Swa-\nfnes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Joabs Zerujas Dehls\ntahzis ſkaitiht/ bet wiꞥſch to-\npabeidse/ tapehz ka zaur to le-\nDuſniba pahr Israēlu nah-\ntadeht tas ſkaitihts Pulks net-\npe aprakſtihts ta Kehnina D-\nwida Laiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pahr tahm Kehn-\nMantahm bija Asmawets V-\neka Dehls/ un pahr tahm S-\nmes Mantahm Bilsfahtos\nZeeinōs/ un Pillis bija Jonat-\nllsja Dehls.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
